timo-a-lomboker - Timo A Lomboker

USAGE:
    timo-a-lomboker <java-file>

DESCRIPTION:
    Analyze Java file using Timo A Lomboker tool to reduce
    boilerplate code and generate summary statistics.

ARGUMENTS:
    java-file
        Java file to analyze (required)

ANALYSIS PERFORMED:
    - Reduce getter methods
    - Reduce setter methods  
    - Reduce equalsAndHashCode
    - Reduce toString
    - Reduce no-args-constructor
    - Generate summary

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-dev-java-timo-a-lomboker-jdk JDK
        JDK to use for analysis

    -conf-dev-java-timo-a-lomboker-jar PATH
        Path to Timo A Lomboker JAR

EXAMPLES:
    timo-a-lomboker MyClass.java
    timo-a-lomboker src/main/java/com/example/Model.java
